  array('id' => '21','user_id' => '10001','category_id' => '31','return_policy' => '1','category_path' => '5,28,31','title' => 'Lomo LC-Wide 35mm Camera','description' => '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Say hello to the latest innovation in the LOMO legacy, the ultra-talented LC-Wide.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Featuring a specially designed 17mm Minigon 1 Ultra-Wide-Angle lens, every photo is taken to the widest extremes.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Add a whole new dimension to your Lomographic shots with a choice of 3 different photo formats of like full, square or half-format.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">With unlimited multiple exposures, auto-exposure settings, lightning-quick focusing and a tripod thread, you\'re looking at a true analogue superstar.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Minigon Ultra-Wide Lens: </strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Developed specially for the LC-Wide; as its name suggests, the 17mm Minigon Ultra-Wide Lens takes stunning wide-angle photos.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Format Frenzy: </strong>Choose between full, square or half-format shots at the click of a switch.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Classic Lomographic Look: </strong>The Minigon lens delivers superb vignettes, mind-blowing color saturation and knockout contrast.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Lightning-fast zone Focusing: </strong>Easily pick your focus distance and get as close as 0.4m to your subject.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Simple Multiple and long exposures: </strong>Take unlimited multiple exposure shots and use the included cable release thread for effortless long exposures.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Film ISO range from 100-1600: </strong>Whether you pick a low or high ISO film, the LC-Wide will have a setting to match.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Use 35mm Film: </strong>Takes all types of 35mm film including color negative, slide, black and white and redscale.</p>','total_quantity' => '5','sold' => '0','exchange_policy' => '1','policy_description' => '','video_mp4' => NULL,'video_webm' => NULL,'video_thumb' => NULL,'views_count' => '0','likes_count' => '0','status' => 'Active','admin_status' => 'Approved','sold_out' => 'No','cash_on_store' => 'No','cash_on_delivery' => 'No','is_featured' => 'Yes','is_popular' => 'Yes','is_recommend' => 'Yes','is_editor' => 'Yes','is_header' => 'Yes','created_at' => '2017-09-19 18:35:20','updated_at' => '2020-01-31 19:46:10'),
  array('id' => '22','user_id' => '10001','category_id' => '31','return_policy' => '1','category_path' => '5,28,31','title' => 'Fujifilm X100S Digital Camera','description' => '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The Fujifilm X100S Digital Camera features a 16 megapixel APS-C-sized X-Trans CMOS II sensor and an EXR Processor II image processor to provide high quality imagery and exceptional camera performance.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The combination of the sensor and processor enables a native sensitivity range from ISO 200-6400, which is further expandable to ISO 100-25600. Fujifilm\'s proprietary X-Trans sensor uses a unique randomized pixel array in order to avoid the use of a resolution-reducing optical low-pass filter, therefore providing images with the utmost sharpness and clarity.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">This imaging system is benefitted by the Intelligent Hybrid AF system, which uses both contrast- and phase-detection methods to acquire focus quickly and accurately. The EXR Processor II also delivers fast performance speeds to all aspects of the camera, ranging from quick startup and shutter lag times to a fast 6fps continuous shooting rate.</p>','total_quantity' => '25','sold' => '0','exchange_policy' => '1','policy_description' => '','video_mp4' => NULL,'video_webm' => NULL,'video_thumb' => NULL,'views_count' => '0','likes_count' => '0','status' => 'Active','admin_status' => 'Approved','sold_out' => 'No','cash_on_store' => 'No','cash_on_delivery' => 'No','is_featured' => 'Yes','is_popular' => 'Yes','is_recommend' => 'Yes','is_editor' => 'Yes','is_header' => 'Yes','created_at' => '2017-09-19 18:41:33','updated_at' => '2020-01-31 19:46:22'),
  array('id' => '23','user_id' => '10001','category_id' => '32','return_policy' => '2','category_path' => '5,28,32','title' => 'Sony Alpha a7R Mirrorless Digital Camera','description' => '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Please your clients and preserve important moments by shooting with the Sony Alpha a7R, which features a 36.4-megapixel Exmor CMOS sensor that enables accurate image reproduction and HD video capture.</p>
