  array('id' => '31','user_id' => '10001','category_id' => '7','return_policy' => '2','category_path' => '7','title' => 'The SteakStones Sizzling Starter Set','description' => '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The SteakStones Sizzling Starter Set is a great introduction to the benefits and features of Hot Stone Cooking. Perfect for a sizzling selection of Scallops and King Prawns with some chilli sauce and lemon mayonnaise or perhaps some mixed meat and fish skewers, the dry heat of the stone sears in the natural moisture and flavours of your chosen cut and with no oils or fats required it’s a fresh, fun and healthy way to cook every bite to perfection.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">How to Use<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;" />Simply heat the stone (on the hob or stove, under the grill, in the oven or on your barbecue], add a selection of sauces or other accompaniments and present your chosen cut of meat, fish or vegetables on the sizzling stone for you and your guests to enjoy cooking every bite exactly as you like. We recommend a pair of our top quality oven gloves are purchased with this product.</p>','total_quantity' => '7','sold' => '0','exchange_policy' => '2','policy_description' => '','video_mp4' => NULL,'video_webm' => NULL,'video_thumb' => NULL,'views_count' => '0','likes_count' => '0','status' => 'Active','admin_status' => 'Approved','sold_out' => 'No','cash_on_store' => 'No','cash_on_delivery' => 'No','is_featured' => 'Yes','is_popular' => 'Yes','is_recommend' => 'Yes','is_editor' => 'Yes','is_header' => 'Yes','created_at' => '2017-09-19 20:56:27','updated_at' => '2020-01-31 20:03:55'),
  array('id' => '32','user_id' => '10002','category_id' => '8','return_policy' => '3','category_path' => '8','title' => 'Vega Concrete TV Stand','description' => '<p><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial;">This piece has the patina of the Industrial Age. Perhaps its the concrete shelves mixed with metal frame. Whichever, this is a mighty cool media console that will serve as a television screen stand and hold anything from books to rest of your electronic components. TV stand measures 67.5"W x 14"D x 23.5"H</span></p>','total_quantity' => '7','sold' => '1','exchange_policy' => '3','policy_description' => '','video_mp4' => NULL,'video_webm' => NULL,'video_thumb' => NULL,'views_count' => '0','likes_count' => '0','status' => 'Active','admin_status' => 'Approved','sold_out' => 'No','cash_on_store' => 'No','cash_on_delivery' => 'No','is_featured' => 'Yes','is_popular' => 'Yes','is_recommend' => 'Yes','is_editor' => 'Yes','is_header' => 'Yes','created_at' => '2017-09-19 21:03:14','updated_at' => '2020-02-03 18:31:26'),
  array('id' => '33','user_id' => '10002','category_id' => '26','return_policy' => '2','category_path' => '4,23,26','title' => 'Otto Fan','description' => '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">When things start heating up, Otto can help with a gentle breeze or it can generate a gale! Thanks to the adjustable industrial fan, the air circulation can easily be varied, as well as the height - Otto is fitted with height-adjustable feet.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Otto is made of eco-friendly Bamboo, perfect for everyday lasting beauty. The rich hues of the wood are enhanced and protected by oil varnish. High grade steel balances the natural form of the wood with modern contemporary style.</p>
