  array('id' => '37','user_id' => '10002','category_id' => '12','return_policy' => '2','category_path' => '12','title' => 'Lion Papertrophy','description' => '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; font-weight: normal !important;">Are pictures on the wall too boring for you? Then this *Lion Wall Trophy* is just the right thing for you.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The Lion Wall Trophy is made from high quality 230g paper.* Of course the lion is produced from FSC certified *environmentally friendly* paper.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">You receive ready *cut and pre-folded* parts that you just have to stick together.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The paper model *Lion* Wall Trophy has extremely high-quality folded edges (*no perforations!*) and is made of *paper that is dyed right through* giving a high quality look.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Assembly of the Lion Wall Trophy fake taxidermy is very easy and does not require any complicated instructions. You simply have to stick the numbered parts to the marked parts. It is very easy and requires no special qualifications other than a little patience.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Each Lion is ready to ship within 24 hours.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; quotes: none; font-style: normal; outline: none; line-height: 18px; color: #383d48; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The Lion Wall Trophy is lovingly produced in Berlin.</p>
